{"tid":969943,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【又一個離巢】多圖 大台出道轉眼十六年 34歲沈卓盈回復自由身","createTime":"2019-01-05T12:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T09:33:39.000Z","uid":121464,"like":411,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"d5c34b608c0ae19bebdadc4a3bd6e2ae21808781","tid":969943,"uid":121464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T12:11:22.000Z","msg":"現年34歲嘅大台小花沈卓盈（沈大師），2002年參加大台第四屆《TVB周刊》Cover Girl選舉奪冠入行，一做便16年，佢去年底約滿，深思熟慮後決定唔再續約向外闖，沈大師今日喺Instagram貼文，宣佈回復自由身。<br />\n<br />\n沈大師貼出一張華麗轉身甫士照片後，佢留言：「時間飛逝，轉眼間已16個年頭，回想當初參加《TVB周刊》所舉辦的Cover Girl選舉而入行，不經不覺喺呢個大家庭保護下慢慢成長，喺度讓我衷心多謝公司一路以來對我的栽培同愛護，沒有公司，也沒有今天的我。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190105/59107377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190105%2F59107377&d=YUUKqXhtvJWnT3ADY%2FvlnJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=8bc8cdda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190105%2F59107377&h=b3133829\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190105/59107377</a><br />\n<br />\n加載<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jV8ZRD8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjV8ZRD8.png&h=3f258834&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iqdK2LP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiqdK2LP.png&h=b271f1a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wj2WTSu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwj2WTSu.png&h=252abd72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mmg1kxv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMmg1kxv.png&h=2ad2964a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3m1kxw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3m1kxw.png&h=7b802b19&s={SIZE}\"